  "content": "<div id=\"SO_ArmorClassModifiers\">\n<table class=\"inner\" style=\"height: 245px; width: 537px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 16px;\"><strong>Defender is...</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 146.667px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Melee</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 155.667px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Ranged</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 16px;\">Behind cover</td>\n<td style=\"width: 146.667px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 155.667px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 19px;\">Blinded</td>\n<td style=\"width: 146.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 155.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 16px;\">Concealed or invisible</td>\n<td style=\"width: 302.333px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\" colspan=\"2\">See Concealment</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 19px;\">Cowering</td>\n<td style=\"width: 146.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 155.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 19px;\">Entangled</td>\n<td style=\"width: 146.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">+0<sup>2</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 155.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">+0<sup>2</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 19px;\">Flat-footed</td>\n<td style=\"width: 146.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">+0<sup>1</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 155.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">+0<sup>1</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 16px;\">Grappling (but the attacker is not)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 146.667px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+0</td>\n<td style=\"width: 155.667px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 19px;\">Helpless</td>\n<td style=\"width: 146.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">-4<sup>3</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 155.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">+0<sup>3</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 16px;\">Kneeling or sitting</td>\n<td style=\"width: 146.667px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 155.667px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 19px;\">Pinned</td>\n<td style=\"width: 146.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">-4<sup>3</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 155.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">+0<sup>3</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 16px;\">Prone</td>\n<td style=\"width: 146.667px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 155.667px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 16px;\">Squeezing through a space</td>\n<td style=\"width: 146.667px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 155.667px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 229.667px; height: 19px;\">Stunned</td>\n<td style=\"width: 146.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 155.667px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n1 The defender loses any Dexterity bonus to AC.<br />2 An entangled character takes a &ndash;4 penalty to Dexterity.<br />3 The defender is flat-footed and cannot add his Dex bonus to AC.</div>",
